WEBVTT

00:00:01.020 --> 00:00:06.420
Hi, I have another dream that the Lord

00:00:04.440 --> 00:00:09.179
wanted me to tell you all about.

00:00:06.420 --> 00:00:11.340
Now, this one's pretty serious—well,

00:00:09.179 --> 00:00:14.700
all of them have been serious, but this

00:00:11.340 --> 00:00:16.500
one was really on my heart this week.

00:00:16.500 --> 00:00:20.400
It started out as I was praying over

00:00:19.140 --> 00:00:23.160
the wars

00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:27.439
and what's going on in Ukraine,

00:00:23.160 --> 00:00:31.140
and the Lord showed me a massive storm

00:00:27.439 --> 00:00:35.399
on the East Coast of America.

00:00:31.140 --> 00:00:39.059
It was as dark as you could

00:00:35.399 --> 00:00:42.719
see through, like a dark, dark purple

00:00:39.059 --> 00:00:45.300
storm, and the lightning

00:00:42.719 --> 00:00:46.140
was striking through it. It

00:00:45.300 --> 00:00:48.779
was

00:00:46.140 --> 00:00:52.260
very scary-looking in the natural

00:00:48.780 --> 00:00:56.039
to look at the storm, and it was

00:00:52.260 --> 00:00:59.640
getting closer and closer.

00:00:56.039 --> 00:01:01.620
When I pray, I see in the

00:00:59.640 --> 00:01:03.960
spirit and the Lord shows me, and the

00:01:01.620 --> 00:01:06.179
storm gets closer and closer. The last time I saw

00:01:03.960 --> 00:01:08.580
it, the rain was coming; I

00:01:06.180 --> 00:01:11.100
could see the

00:01:08.580 --> 00:01:12.960
raindrops

00:01:11.100 --> 00:01:14.520
coming out of

00:01:12.960 --> 00:01:18.960
the storm.

00:01:14.520 --> 00:01:22.920
But the Lord showed me this massive wall. The

00:01:18.960 --> 00:01:23.580
wall

00:01:23.580 --> 00:01:31.798
was probably

00:01:27.380 --> 00:01:34.140
five feet thick, maybe more, and it

00:01:31.799 --> 00:01:37.140
was made of

00:01:34.140 --> 00:01:41.700
humongous bricks; it went up as high

00:01:37.140 --> 00:01:43.259
as probably thirty feet, or maybe even

00:01:41.700 --> 00:01:44.939
bigger, like a several-story

00:01:43.259 --> 00:01:47.340
building.

00:01:47.340 --> 00:01:54.840
On this side of it, I could see

00:01:52.020 --> 00:01:56.640
light coming out of it.

00:01:54.840 --> 00:01:59.939
The light was shining through the clouds

00:01:56.640 --> 00:02:02.159
and it was beautiful. There was a

00:01:59.939 --> 00:02:04.380
stream going through on

00:02:02.159 --> 00:02:05.939
this side of the wall, and there was a

00:02:05.939 --> 00:02:11.640
little hut—a little house

00:02:09.060 --> 00:02:14.760
with a picnic table outside of it with

00:02:11.640 --> 00:02:17.940
green grass—and there was a

00:02:14.760 --> 00:02:21.899
little stove, a chimney

00:02:17.940 --> 00:02:24.060
stove with smoke coming out of

00:02:21.900 --> 00:02:26.360
it, and you could smell the smell of

00:02:24.060 --> 00:02:26.360
bread.

00:02:28.379 --> 00:02:33.480
The Lord told me—I said, "Lord, what is

00:02:31.319 --> 00:02:39.359
this that You're showing me?"—and He said,

00:02:33.480 --> 00:02:41.340
"Brandon, this is Psalm 91 and Psalm 23,

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:44.459
both together."He

00:02:41.340 --> 00:02:47.580
said, "If you stay in the secret place

00:02:44.459 --> 00:02:50.519
of the Most High and you abide in that

00:02:47.580 --> 00:02:53.220
shadow of the Almighty, none of that

00:02:50.519 --> 00:02:55.260
storm is going to come near you. But

00:02:53.220 --> 00:02:59.220
you're going to have to stay close to Me

00:02:55.260 --> 00:03:02.940
and get those scriptures, Psalm 91 and Psalm

00:02:59.220 --> 00:03:06.420
23, deep down in your heart. It has

00:03:02.940 --> 00:03:07.500
to become a Rhema word inside of you for

00:03:06.420 --> 00:03:11.099
what's coming.

00:03:07.500 --> 00:03:13.739
You have to know that word, Psalm 91 and Psalm

00:03:11.099 --> 00:03:15.780
23. You can't just read, 'The

00:03:13.739 --> 00:03:17.819
Lord is my shepherd; I shall not want.'You

00:03:15.780 --> 00:03:19.980
can't just flippantly echo it by

00:03:17.819 --> 00:03:22.260
just reading it off."You have

00:03:19.980 --> 00:03:25.140
to meditate on the pages until

00:03:22.260 --> 00:03:28.319
it becomes a revelation to you and

00:03:25.140 --> 00:03:31.200
gets deep inside your spirit, so

00:03:28.319 --> 00:03:34.560
that it is a sword when it comes out of

00:03:31.200 --> 00:03:37.859
your mouth. In James 4:7,

00:03:34.560 --> 00:03:41.340
you submit yourself unto God, resist the

00:03:37.860 --> 00:03:43.680
devil, and he will flee from you.

00:03:41.340 --> 00:03:46.080
You have to understand that word and

00:03:43.680 --> 00:03:48.180
get a revelation of it, so that when you

00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:50.519
are submitting yourself unto God and

00:03:48.180 --> 00:03:52.080
resisting the devil, he will flee

00:03:50.519 --> 00:03:54.540
from you. You must have a

00:03:52.080 --> 00:03:56.700
revelation of it, because if it's not a Rhema

00:03:54.540 --> 00:03:58.560
word inside of you, you might as

00:03:56.700 --> 00:04:00.839
well be singing "Twinkle, Twinkle, Little Star,"because

00:03:58.560 --> 00:04:02.819
it's not going to have any

00:04:00.840 --> 00:04:05.360
power behind it since you're just flippantly

00:04:02.819 --> 00:04:08.220
saying things. I can quote

00:04:05.360 --> 00:04:10.980
scripture all day long; the devil knows

00:04:08.220 --> 00:04:12.720
the scripture, and he understands the

00:04:10.980 --> 00:04:15.480
scripture better than a lot of

00:04:12.720 --> 00:04:18.720
Christians do, but it's whenever the word

00:04:15.480 --> 00:04:21.659
becomes a Rhema to you that it becomes

00:04:18.720 --> 00:04:24.419
revelation knowledge that comes out of

00:04:21.660 --> 00:04:26.400
your spirit and becomes powerful. That is

00:04:24.419 --> 00:04:29.580
what you need to know: whenever

00:04:26.400 --> 00:04:32.880
that word becomes powerful to you, that's when

00:04:29.580 --> 00:04:34.979
you're going to get results. That

00:04:32.880 --> 00:04:36.719
is

00:04:34.979 --> 00:04:39.060
one of the things the Lord told

00:04:36.720 --> 00:04:41.759
me to tell you when I was praying this

00:04:39.060 --> 00:04:43.919
morning, so I'm going to end this

00:04:41.759 --> 00:04:47.220
video there. I hope you have a blessed

00:04:43.919 --> 00:04:50.099
day. No weapon formed against you

00:04:47.220 --> 00:04:51.540
is going to prosper; you have to get that

00:04:50.100 --> 00:04:53.460
inside of you

00:04:51.540 --> 00:04:54.620
for when the storms are coming.

00:04:54.620 --> 00:05:01.759
Greater is he that is in you than he

00:04:57.660 --> 00:05:01.759
that is in the world. Have a blessed day.

